# Goose proxy LiteLLM config files. Current code writes these under
# $XDG_STATE_HOME/ngb-agent-orchestrator/proxy-sessions/ (outside the
# repo), but stale processes started before the fix may have left files
# in the repo root; the rule below keeps them out of commits.
goose_proxy_*.yaml
